<h3 id="看看gcn的输入是啥">看看GCN的输入是啥</h3>
<p>Given a graph $G = (V, E)$ , a GCN takes as input:</p>

<ul>
  <li>adjacency matrix $\mathbf{A}$ of $G$.   <em>N</em> × <em>N</em></li>
  <li>an input feature matrix, $N × F⁰$ feature matrix, $\mathbf{X}$,
    <ul>
      <li>where <em>N</em> is the number of nodes and</li>
      <li><em>F⁰</em> is the number of input features for each node</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

